Vocal Mumias East MP Benjamin Washiali Has Said He Went Into Hiding On Saturday After He Realized Police Officers We After Him. Washiali?Led Tanga Tanga Team Had Planned A Parallel Rally At Mumias Bomani Grounds To Counter Bukhungu BBI Meeting. His Colleagues Had Alleged That Washiali Was Abducted To Stop Them From Proceeding With Their Meeting That Police Had Already Revoked Its Permit. ANC And Ford Kenya Parties Have Continued To Distance Themselves From Mumias Meeting Alleging Tanga Tanga Team Had Dragged Them Into Anti BBI Campaigns.